<ul>
<li><a href="megatrends-corporate-futurists-beware-moves-field-and-more#megatrends">Hot Topic: Megatrends and Future Research</a></li>
<li><a href="megatrends-corporate-futurists-beware-moves-field-and-more#news">Futurism in the News: Forbes on Corporate Futurists</a></li>
